sequenceDiagram
	participant Transaction FE
	participant zkpID Auth
    participant zkpID
    participant Alice Acct
    participant PrivacyPool Acct
    participant Bob Acct
    participant KYC Provider
        Transaction FE->>Alice Acct: wallet connect
        Alice Acct->>Transaction FE: wallet address
        Transaction FE->>Transaction FE: check amount
        alt amount > 15 Aleo
            Transaction FE->>zkpID: check address kyc status
            zkpID->>Transaction FE: kyc status
            alt kyc status false
                Transaction FE->>Transaction FE: new tab w/ wallet address
                Transaction FE->>KYC Provider: req iframe for kyc check {addr}
                KYC Provider->>Transaction FE: provide KYC iframe
                KYC Provider->>zkpID: kyc result
                loop every 3s
                    Transaction FE->>zkpID: check address kyc status
                    zkpID->>Transaction FE: kyc status
                end
            else kyc status true
                Transaction FE->>Transaction FE: create trx {amount, Bob, sig(addr)}
                Transaction FE->>PrivacyPool Acct: send pub trx
                PrivacyPool Acct->>PrivacyPool Acct: check sig
                alt sig true
                    PrivacyPool Acct->>PrivacyPool Acct: swap to private
                    PrivacyPool Acct->>Bob Acct: send priv trx
                else sig false
                    PrivacyPool Acct->>Alice Acct: send pub trx
                end
            end
        else amount < 15 Aleo
            Transaction FE->>Transaction FE: create trx {amount, Bob}
            Transaction FE->>PrivacyPool Acct: send pub trx
            PrivacyPool Acct->>PrivacyPool Acct: swap to private
            PrivacyPool Acct->>Bob Acct: send priv trx
        end
